---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="3D Scanning & Drone Equipment Comparisons"
  description="Compare latest 3D scanning and drone equipment. Matterport Pro 3 vs Pro 2, Trimble X12 vs Leica BLK360, LiDAR vs Photogrammetry, and more."
  keywords="3d scanner comparison, drone comparison, matterport comparison, equipment comparison"
>
  <main class="min-h-screen">
    <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-900 to-blue-700 text-white py-20">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
        <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-4">Equipment Comparisons</h1>
        <p class="text-xl max-w-2xl mx-auto">Compare 3D scanners, drones, and mapping methods to find the best solution for your project</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-16">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-12 text-gray-900">Equipment Comparisons</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <a href="/comparisons/matterport-pro-3-vs-pro-2" class="bg-white border-2 border-blue-600 rounded-lg p-8 hover:shadow-xl transition">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3 text-gray-900">Matterport Pro 3 vs Pro 2</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Pro 3 is 2.75x more accurate (±20mm vs ±55mm) - see why we upgraded</p>
            <p class="text-blue-600 font-semibold">Read Comparison →</p>
          </a>

          <a href="/comparisons/trimble-x12-vs-leica-blk360" class="bg-white border-2 border-gray-200 hover:border-blue-600 rounded-lg p-8 hover:shadow-xl transition">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3 text-gray-900">Trimble X12 vs Leica BLK360</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Compare range (365m vs 60m) and accuracy for professional scanning</p>
            <p class="text-blue-600 font-semibold">Read Comparison →</p>
          </a>

          <a href="/comparisons/lidar-vs-photogrammetry" class="bg-white border-2 border-gray-200 hover:border-blue-600 rounded-lg p-8 hover:shadow-xl transition">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3 text-gray-900">LiDAR vs Photogrammetry</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">When to use each method for drone mapping and surveying</p>
            <p class="text-blue-600 font-semibold">Read Comparison →</p>
          </a>

          <a href="/comparisons/dji-matrice-400-vs-matrice-350" class="bg-white border-2 border-gray-200 hover:border-blue-600 rounded-lg p-8 hover:shadow-xl transition">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3 text-gray-900">DJI Matrice 400 vs 350</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">What changed in the 2025 release - improved flight time, range, weather resistance</p>
            <p class="text-blue-600 font-semibold">Read Comparison →</p>
          </a>

          <a href="/comparisons/trimble-x12-vs-matterport-pro-3" class="bg-white border-2 border-gray-200 hover:border-blue-600 rounded-lg p-8 hover:shadow-xl transition">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3 text-gray-900">Trimble X12 vs Matterport Pro 3</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Choose the right scanner: survey-grade precision vs virtual tour speed</p>
            <p class="text-blue-600 font-semibold">Read Comparison →</p>
          </a>

          <a href="/comparisons/trimble-x12-vs-x9-vs-x7" class="bg-white border-2 border-gray-200 hover:border-blue-600 rounded-lg p-8 hover:shadow-xl transition">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3 text-gray-900">Trimble X12 vs X9 vs X7</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Trimble laser scanner lineup compared - range differences explained</p>
            <p class="text-blue-600 font-semibold">Read Comparison →</p>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-16 bg-blue-600 text-white text-center">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Questions About Equipment?</h2>
        <p class="text-xl mb-6">We use the latest 2025 technology for all projects</p>
        <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-white text-blue-600 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-bold">Get Free Consultation</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>

